original_title: ONE Friday Fights 14: Gingsanglek vs. Chorfah
overview: ONE Friday Fights 14: Gingsanglek vs. Chorfah (also known as ONE Lumpinee 14) was a combat sports event produced by ONE Championship that took place on April 28, 2023, at Lumpinee Boxing Stadium in Bangkok, Thailand. A 132 pounds catchweight muay thai bout between Gingsanglek Tor.Laksong and Chorfah Tor.Sangtiennoi served as the event headliner.
title: ONE Friday Fights 14: Gingsanglek vs. Chorfah
